---

Test Cases (Validation)

| Test Category | Input Action | Expected Result | Status |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Conflict Detection** | Book 10:00-11:00 over 10:30-11:30 | System rejects or triggers preemption. | PASSED |
| **Preemption** | Priority 3 Event over Priority 1 Event | Priority 1 Event is moved to next free slot. | PASSED |
| **Queue Overflow** | Add 11th person to 10-cap room | Participant moved to waitlist. | PASSED |
| **Persistence** | Save data, Restart, Load data | All events and queues restored exactly. | PASSED |

